 | image1    = Rudy Gobert 2015 (cropped).jpg
 | width1    = 100
 | caption1  = [[鲁迪·戈贝尔|戈贝尔]]
 | image2    = Donovan Mitchell Utah 2018 (cropped).jpg
 | width2    = 140
 | caption2  = [[多诺万·米切尔|米切尔]]
